caller_intent: The caller wanted to make a payment for her auto insurance policy.
resolution_steps: Agent asked for the caller's name (Darlene Duncan).
Processed the payment and confirmed its success.
Offered confirmation number or email receipt; caller opted for email.
summary: Darlene Duncan called to pay her auto insurance. The agent processed the $330.24 payment using her credit card details, confirmed the transaction, and sent an email receipt. The caller did not request further assistance.
